Mathematics</link> there also. Robert Prim worked at <university wordnetid="108286163" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../922/23922.xml">
Princeton University</link></university>
 from 1948 until 1949 as a research associate. </p>
